{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HGNkBXHhxmeB2yhWHPBAE9","type":"tool_result","content":"  2620→\n  2621→## Updated End-of-Day Sprint Summary — 2026-03-25 (Final, Session 16)\n  2622→\n  2623→| Metric | Value |\n  2624→|--------|-------|\n  2625→| Stories completed | 65/66 (98.5%) |\n  2626→| Epics completed | 15/16 (Epic 14 has 1 story remaining) |\n  2627→| Stories completed today | 10 (sessions 1-6) |\n  2628→| Total sessions today | 16 (loops 1-16) |\n  2629→| Productive sessions | 6 (sessions 1-6) |\n  2630→| No-op sessions | 10 (sessions 7-16) |\n  2631→| Wasted session ratio | 62.5% (10/16) |\n  2632→| Remaining blocker | 14-4-observability-backend-choice (Docker keychain, retry-exhausted, 10/10) |\n  2633→| Circuit breaker status | CLOSED (broken -- does not detect no-ops due to ralph state file changes) |\n  2634→| Test suite | 3799 tests passing, 97.1% coverage |\n  2635→| Critical fix needed | Ralph loop termination for \"effectively complete\" sprints |\n  2636→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01RUZ3ox2TBirAWSN6pwaHJb","session_id":"95666539-e92c-435f-b7f3-cd5139d3b996","uuid":"9c066f10-ca71-42ad-82a7-a5fb19c14fb3","timestamp":"2026-03-25T07:45:38.267Z"}
